Have you wanted to learn pole but didn’t know where to start?! ⁣
.⁣
.⁣
👏🏾 Here 👏🏾 Is 👏🏾 Your 👏🏾 Chance! 👏🏾👏🏾👏🏾⁣
.⁣
.⁣
I teamed up with @rackstoriches to create a course designed for upcoming dancers to receive expert knowledge from an industry instructor! ✨ This course will teach you everything you need to know to secure your audition AND kill the stage from 6 feet away 🙌🏾! #SpreadTheWord #TellAFriend 
#YungPoleMaster

node.text:
My last performance before COVID-19 stopped everything! (shoutout to @itsasiab for my custom outfit though!) ⁣
⁣
During testing times I love to look at videos like this to remind me being black is BEAUTIFUL. I love my community, my skin complexion, our POWER... 🙏🏾✊🏾⁣ ⁣
If you are interested in supporting my businesses or other BPOC, feel free to DM me! I’ll send you my current @pytfitnessllc class schedule and information about my upcoming pole tutorials 🙏🏾✨

node.text:
𝗪𝐇𝐀𝐓𝐂𝐇𝐔 𝐃𝐎𝐈𝐍 𝗪𝐈𝐓 𝐀𝐋𝐋𝐃𝐀𝐓 𝐀𝐒𝐒???⁣
⁣
Thank you to @soldiers_of_pole_ for creating a space bringing dancers and allies together in unity for a spectacular stripper showcase. I am honored to have been selected to hit my 2-step one time for the one time... 🙌🏾 ⁣
⁣
Before I went on I was mad nervous if I chose the perfect song or had the appropriate outfit on (but fuck it, it looks good and i know my ass is out! Don’t look too hard 🤣). After my friends reassured me I was ok I went out there and blacked out. ⁣
⁣
Well, until I got smacked in the face with money. 2020 looking bright for us. Yes, you and I! #TeamFuckItUp 🤪⁣
⁣
👙: @itsasiab ⁣
⁣

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Miles Woods IV 💫 (Pole Master) on July 28, 2021 tagging @cedarpoint. May be an image of one or more people and outdoors.

node.text:
most likely to cause a scene @cedarpoint ❤️ 

When I’m not on the pole teaching and trapping I thoroughly enjoy traveling. I’m that friend who knows all the good eats and museums, best theme parks, nightclubs, hotels and more. My Yelp and YouTube game is out of this world! 😂😂

I encourage all my friends, family and followers to take a trip to a place you’ve always wanted to go. Even if it’s around the corner, GO. (and tbh the local spots you’ve never been to always hit!) 

Life is too short to scroll on TikTok and Twitter all day. Live yo’ best authentic life and cherish each day you have on this floating rock. Every day is extra! ❤️💯 Love y’all 🙏🏾

🎶 sensual seduction 🎶 

fun fact: @sweetmscandace and I met on my first night dancing in Los Angeles and became inseparable. No cap! 

“I’ll teach you how to pole if you teach me how to vogue.” were the first words Candace said to me. 

I replied “say less!!” cutting her off immediately. 🗣

That summer (2015) she plugged me with my first studio job at Secret making us brother and sister. IYKYK 💯

love you big sis 🖤

node.text:
Mood all #pride season. ❤️🧡🧡💚💙💜

Wear your fave bathing suit. 
Take shots like a champ, virgin shots count too.
And please bust the splits baby,
it’s that time. 💯

Current life in a nutshell 💗

Sorry I don’t post on my page often. My Aquarius moon keeps me in my own world. I love y’all though 🥲🥲

And as always I’m teaching, working, elevating... living my life to the fullest.

Lastly, if you’re reading this be open to receiving all the positive vibes I have for you. Love and light 🥰✨🙏🏾

node.text:
Say hello to your newest @theabbeyweho dancer! ❤️🙏🏾 

Y’all it feels so good to be dancing in West Hollywood again. I’m thankful, thrilled and blessed to serve for the masses every weekend! It’s giving 💡🎥 🍿 

I’ll be available for money showers tomorrow from 6-10pm and Friday night 8-midnight. Come have a drink and say hi! 💗🙏🏾❤️ 😉😇
